  <Key>BIGGERTHEYARE</Key>
  <Name>The Bigger They Are...</Name>
  <Description>Once per game session as an action, the character may spend 2 Destiny Points, nominate one vehicle, starship, or living creature of silhouette 2 or smaller that he can see, and make a [B]Hard ([DI][DI][DI]) Knowledge (Warfare) check[b]. If he succeeds, for the next 3 rounds, he and each other friendly character within medium range of him ignore the target's armor (or soak, if it is a living creature) when inflicting damage on the target with non-vehicle/starship weapons.</Description>
